maml:description.maml:para: Sets the full path for the log file.

The Set-AppSenseDesktopNowLogPath cmdlet sets the full path for the log file. It should be noted that only messages generated directly by this module will be logged. Any messages shown by native (AppSense or Microsoft) will not be logged.
Full path to the location to store the log file.
When provided the time will also be output to any verbosely written line.
Full path to the location to store the log file.
When provided the time will also be output to any verbosely written line.
Returns $true when the path has been successfully set and $false if an error occurred. If $false is returned check the $error variable for details.

dev:remarks.maml:para: This example will set the log file destination to "C:\Temp\AppSenseDesktopNowLogFile.txt".
